data.description:
Come home to a vacation everyday.Beautiful waterfront paradise with 123 ft of waterfront. Inside, you will walk right into a stunning view of the spectacular Cowpen Lake covering almost 700 acres from every main area of the house. The best view from the glass enclosed Florida room is absolutely perfect for viewing all of the gorgeous wildlife that Florida has to offer. You'll get to sit back with your morning coffee or tea while you enjoy watching the cranes, ducks, and even bald eagles soar over and splash.
It's easy to see that this home has been built for entertainment and relaxation with all of the features and space offered inside including the 4 bedrooms, a private study above the master, 3 and half bathrooms two of which have huge, jetted tubs, beautiful kitchen offering all of the counterspace you could possibly need and stainless-steel appliances.
Outside, the property offers you and your guests 2 terraces, a lighted tile shower, additional building with a half bath large enough for your jet ski and more, and a private, concrete dock leading out to the water from a sand beach. Do you require even more space? Along with everything else this property offers, there is a  36X30 Morton building on slab with power.There is so much more to see. SURVEY AVAIL. 4 year old roof. Don't sleep on the house of your dreams. Schedule your private tour now.
